      • getFlags

        public ArrayList<String> getFlags()

        Retrieve a list of flags that indicate what items the upgrade component may be applied to.

        Possible values are:

        • HeavyArmor
        • MediumArmor
        • LightArmor
        • Axe
        • Dagger
        • Focus
        • Greatsword
        • Hammer
        • Harpoon
        • LongBow
        • Mace
        • Pistol
        • Rifle
        • Scepter
        • Shield
        • ShortBow
        • Speargun
        • Staff
        • Torch
        • Trident
        • Trinket
        • Warhorn
        Returns:
        An array of strings naming item types that the component can upgrade.
